  "remarks": "TV and Radio Company of the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation Zvezda is an organisation controlled by Russia’s Ministry of Defence and financed by the Russian state. The company runs a military-patriotic TV channel “Zvezda” devoted to supporting and promoting Russia’s military, and spreads disinformation and propaganda about Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
